<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A SOLDIER OF THE CROSS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kross sepaih a pang ka hi nam?
 Belam No nung zuiin?
 Amah ziekin ka thuok ngam nam?
 A min ka phuong na dem?

[V2]
 Min achun Min lun ahi,
 Ka sika thi pa chuh;
 Lungsiet na'n lal lukhuk chang di'n,
 Bangcheng thuok zel ingka.

[V3]
 2. Mi dangte'n kipahman sang di'n,
 Theihtawp in a do ui;
 Kei tawilo a mawk a um hi,
 Van a puih ka hi dem?

[V4]
 3. Ka tuok ding gal umlo ahim,
 Galdo lo ding ka him?
 Khawvel gilo ka guol ahim,
 Pathien kawm ei tun ding?

[V5]
 4. Galdo ka, vaihawm ka guot chun,
 Lalpa, ei hihhat in;
 Sem ing ting gimna thuok ngap ka,
 Na Thu a ding zing in.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>316</hymn_number>
</song>